sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Confirm channel deletion
    Frontend->>API: DELETE /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace and channel
    DB-->>API: Workspace and channel found
    API->>DB: Delete channel messages
    API->>DB: Delete channel
    DB-->>API: Deletion committed
    API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
    Frontend->>Frontend: Remove channel from local state
    Frontend-->>Owner: Update channel list
